twitter.description: Chuck Donovan says the Texas abortion-access law before the Supreme Court this week, in the case of Whole Woman’s Health v. Hellerstedt, isn’t forcing clinics to close. They‘re under pressure from declining abortion rates and big Planned Parenthood expansions.
